headline: India sends notices to ride-hailing apps Ola, Uber over 'differential pricing'
summary: An Indian government body has sent notices to ride-hailing firms Ola and Uber over alleged differential pricing for Android and Apple phones, the country's consumer affairs minister, Pralhad Joshi,...
